          <div class="card-body justify-content-center">
            <p>Thanks for visiting our Capstone Project! We are a small team of two programmers from Durham College in Oshawa, Ontario. </p>
            <p>This project started out as an assignment in our Mobile Development class in year 3. We learned Flutter and created an app to help people find vets in their area, and our interest grew from there! We decided to create a responsive web app for our Capstone above one that was strictly mobile because we wanted it to be as accessible as possible for those even without a smartphone. We love our pets and what we do and are excited to bring this idea to life! </p><br>
            
