              <li class="listDecoration"> Select your account theme on the <a class="linkunderline" href="/settings">settings</a> page and show off your favourite pets!</li>
              <li class="listDecoration"> Print a QR code from the <a class="linkunderline" href="/pet_profile">Pet Profile</a> page for your pet and affix it to their collar, harness, or leash!</li>
              <li class="listDecoration"> Interested in your own QR-Code collar? Visit our demo <a class="linkunderline" href="/shop">shop</a> to see what might be available in the future! </li>
